Horrible! Turn it off!

53:41.045 --> 53:44.717
Then about a week later,
everyone was listening to it.

53:44.875 --> 53:48.300
I don't know! I can't really explain
why I am attracted to it like this.

53:48.458 --> 53:51.587
It's just, it hits on something,
it just stroke a nerve.

53:51.750 --> 53:54.720
It brings over a different culture
you don't have here every day.

53:54.875 --> 53:58.960
The lyrics and the language itself
