58:01.833 --> 58:06.259
Maybe I should first explain
how it normally is with a band,

58:06.917 --> 58:12.970
because as a spectator, you don't know
what the problems are on tour.

58:13.125 --> 58:16.550
It's like this, you arrive somewhere,
