it affects your psyche in some way.

58:33.708 --> 58:35.506
I call it the potato syndrome.

58:35.667 --> 58:37.005
You sort of get poured out,

58:37.006 --> 58:40.174
and then have to do what you do every
night, then get collected again.

58:40.333 --> 58:43.132
The only thing you can do,
which I take advantage of,

58:43.292 --> 58:45.670
is watch a lot of films
to learn the language.

58:45.833 --> 58:49.508
A day has 24 hours
and you're on stage for about 1 V2 hours.

58:49.667 --> 58:51.840
The rest of the day is pure boredom.

58:59.208 --> 59:02.587
We have a big toy box with things in it,
