59:02.750 --> 59:05.128
a football, skateboards.

59:07.708 --> 59:11.085
I go with the swim fraction,
which is everyone except Oli and Flake.

59:11.086 --> 59:13.211
The other four go swimming
and I go with them.

59:22.583 --> 59:25.257
Flake always tries desperately
to walk somewhere.

59:27.833 --> 59:32.259
The best part of the day is
when I can wander around.

59:33.000 --> 59:35.628
I can think about things in peace.

59:36.917 --> 59:40.547
When you're so hyped up in the evening,
when so many people applaud you,

59:40.708 --> 59:44.633
the daytime allows you to clarify
why everything is the way it is,

59:44.792 --> 59:47.341
and how to deal with it in the best way.

59:47.500 --> 59:52.041
Because it's hard to feel comfortable
in a foreign country.

59:52.042 --> 59:56.798
I don't really speak the language
so it's nice to have some time

59:56.958 --> 01:00:00.508
to absorb everything in peace
and think about it.

01:00:03.917 --> 01:00:08.999
We have our own cook with us,
because on the first tour of America,

01:00:09.000 --> 01:00:12.049
I realised that in order to be
mentally relaxed,

01:00:12.208 --> 01:00:13.585
