01:00:14.292 --> 01:00:15.885
What a service!

01:00:17.917 --> 01:00:19.169
So that's our daily routine.

01:00:19.708 --> 01:00:21.961
And that's enough to keep
you from going dumb.

01:00:22.667 --> 01:00:25.841
Of course there are
unforeseen incidents on every tour.

