01:56:41.125 --> 01:56:44.129
Which leads me all the way back
to where we started talking.

01:56:44.292 --> 01:56:46.545
There is a level
of authenticity in their music

01:56:46.708 --> 01:56:49.336
and their style and their show
and what they're presenting

01:56:49.500 --> 01:56:52.754
that people are relating to.
And it doesn't matter about their culture,

01:56:52.917 --> 01:56:55.966
it doesn't matter about
what language they speak, they can feel it.

01:56:56.792 --> 01:56:59.420
I couldn't tell you how to do that
in a million years.

01:57:25.958 --> 01:57:30.464
I'd just never seen them
so happy and in such a good place

01:57:30.833 --> 01:57:35.543
and I think that's what happens
when you wait for success to come to you.

01:57:45.958 --> 01:57:50.839
What I learned from it was that we
really tried for a certain period of time

01:57:51.000 --> 01:57:53.719
to establish ourselves here,
with a lot of dedication,

01:57:53.875 --> 01:57:55.297
but nothing ever came of it.

01:57:55.458 --> 01:57:57.756
Only once we were really relaxed about it,

01:57:57.917 --> 01:57:59.005
so typical 'Rammstein, '

01:57:59.006 --> 01:58:02.049
always when we try to will something
into happening, it never works,

01:58:02.208 --> 01:58:04.176
but when we don't want anything,
we get it all.

01:58:45.292 --> 01:58:48.006
The feeling of being from Germany
or being German

01:58:48.007 --> 01:58:51.550
always had a stain on it
that I could sense in some way.

01:58:51.708 --> 01:58:55.041
You always felt somehow guilty.

01:58:55.042 --> 01:58:57.761
And in America I didn't have that anymore.

01:58:57.917 --> 01:58:59.965
People were more open,

01:59:00.167 --> 01:59:05.253
and suddenly certain German virtues
were seen as good.

01:59:05.417 --> 01:59:12.585
Reliability and punctuality
and things like that were appreciated here.

01:59:12.750 --> 01:59:17.961
And for the first time, I really got
a feel for my own home country.

01:59:18.125 --> 01:59:22.210
I had to leave first in order to be OK with
where I come from.

01:59:22.500 --> 01:59:25.424
It was a beautiful experience for me.

